  "title": "art teacher",
  "description": "<p>A challenging and vibrant art education center. We focus on both academic arts learning and art as an expressive language for all learners. We believe that Art is necessary for artgrain and all our team members are art practitioners. We welcome full time and part time art educators to join us.</p>\n<p>Job Scope: Conducting art lessons to children and teens from 3-16 yo - Planning of lessons and materials, upkeeping of teaching resources, room and art materials - Administrative duries to support the teaching and running of the studio, includes reception desk duties - Designing and planning of art projects - Marketing and promotion of various art programmes in the school - Running and planning of holiday projects within Artgrain branches.</p>",
